channel.title: Removing object
channel.description:
I'm putting in the correct stuff to my knowledge from looking at tutorials and such, but i think mine is different this door will not delete or anything, not sure if that's the right way to remove objects but its the only tutorials iv'e seen.
[code]c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(-1, 3061, 3374, 1, 10);[/code]

item.title: Removing object
item.dc:creator: @tank_nation tank nation
item.description:
@tank_nation wrote:

[quote=“sk8rdude461, post:2, topic:551709”]The reason it wont remove the door is because a door is typically object type 0 or 2.

You have the code set to remove object type 10.
c.getPA().checkObjectSpawn(-1, 3061, 3374, 1, 10);
Change the 10 to 0, and if that doesn’t work then increase it by 1 until it does.[/quote]

Okay that worked, now to learn how to open/close doors and make steps work so i can go down them.

Change the 10 to 0, and if that doesn’t work then increase it by 1 until it does.
